more than 3 jobs fall on one day, a '+N more' note appears below the labels. Open the day to see them all."},{"label":"Delivery Labels","value":"When PO deliveries are turned on, each delivery shows a small truck marker, the PO number, and the vendor."},{"label":"Clicking a Day","value":"Click any day to open Day view for that date."}]},{"heading":"Week View","items":[{"label":"Day Headings","value":"Seven columns, each showing a day name and date. Today's column is highlighted."},{"label":"Job Labels","value":"Larger than in Month view. Each shows a priority flag when relevant, the job number, an overdue flag when relevant, the title, and the customer."},{"label":"Delivery Labels","value":"Same as Month view — a truck marker, PO number, and vendor — when PO deliveries are turned on."},{"label":"Clicking a Day Heading","value":"Click a day's heading to open Day view for that date."}]},{"heading":"Day View","items":[{"label":"Day Heading","value":"Shows the full date, how many jobs are due, and how many deliveries are expected when PO deliveries are turned on."},{"label":"Job Cards","value":"A fuller view: job number, title, priority flag, and overdue flag, with a detail line below showing the customer, stage, who it's assigned to, and its priority."},{"label":"Deliveries Section","value":"A separate section below the jobs. Each delivery shows its PO number, vendor, expected date, status, and line count."},{"label":"Nothing Scheduled","value":"When a date has no jobs or deliveries, you'll see a friendly message that nothing is scheduled."}]},{"heading":"Job Label Details","items":[{"label":"Clicking a Job","value":"Click a job in any view to open it on the Kanban board, already selected — that's how you work on a job from the calendar, since the calendar is view-only. Clicking a job opens the board; clicking empty space in a day opens Day view instead."},{"label":"Job Number","value":"Shown up front (for example, 'J-1055'). Identifies the job everywhere in the system